sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as Action Oversight UI
participant BFF as Action Management BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant QUERY as Action Query Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM->>UI: Open project action oversight
UI->>BFF: Load open and closed actions
BFF->>ORCH: Get project oversight view
ORCH->>QUERY: Fetch project action summary
QUERY->>READDB: Query open/closed actions for project
READDB-->>QUERY: Action oversight data
QUERY-->>ORCH: Oversight response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show project-level oversight with latest status
